                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8414" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2114</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1975 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">奈雪寒夜——开放加盟背后的危机</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Cold Night of NAIXUE -- The Crisis Behind Open Franchising</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">徐秀红，陈知源，林芬，肖力业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建农林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">奈雪的茶控股有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">5 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">奈雪的茶；加盟模式；直营模式；多元化；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">NAIXUE, Franchise model, Direct operation model, Diversification</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">奈雪的茶凭借“茶饮+软欧包”双品类模式和独特的消费体验，使其在竞争激烈的茶饮行业中脱颖而出。然而，受差异化战略带来的成本压力及扩张限制，加之激烈的行业竞争，公司年年亏损，面临危机与挑战。尽管公司在2023年宣布开放加盟，但惨遭遇冷。高昂的加盟费用、坚持大店模式、回本速度慢等问题成为加盟商望而却步的原因。对此，奈雪积极调整加盟政策，着力多元化发展，尝试扭转不利局面。但公司的未来依然扑朔迷离，其未来发展仍取决于管理层是否能有效应对市场挑战，找到新茶饮行业竞争的新路径。本案例重点描述奈雪的茶在实施加盟模式战略过程中面临的一系列问题，并引导学生提出解决方案。通过对案例的分析，有助于提升学生在企业加盟模式决策与管理方面的能力，同时引导学生思考不同战略的利弊。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With its dual-category model of “tea + soft omelet” and unique consumer experience, NAIXUE has stood out in the highly competitive tea beverage industry. However, due to the cost pressure and expansion constraints brought about by the differentiation strategy, coupled with the fierce competition in the industry, the company has suffered losses year after year and faced crises and challenges. Although the company announced the opening of franchising in 2023, it was miserably cold. High franchise fees, adherence to the large-store model, and slow payback have become reasons for franchisees to shy away. In response, NAIXUE has been actively adjusting its franchise policy and focusing on diversification in an attempt to reverse the unfavorable situation. However, the company&#39;s future is still confusing, and its future development still depends on whether the management can effectively respond to market challenges and find a new path to compete in the new tea beverage industry. The case focuses on describing a series of problems faced by NAIXUE during the implementation of the franchise model strategy and guides students to propose solutions. By analyzing the case, it helps to improve students&#39; ability in the decision-making and management of corporate franchise model, and at the same time guides students to think about the advantages and disadvantages of different strategies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《市场营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">直营模式和加盟模式的概念、优劣势；加盟商选择加盟的动机；多元化战略；SWOT分析法</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-07</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
